  <summary date="2024-10-04T16:39:15Z" status="Introduced in House">Cease Animal Research Grants Overseas Act of 2023 or the CARGO Act of 2023

This bill prohibits the National Institutes of Health from awarding support for any research that uses live animals unless the research occurs in the United States (including U.S. territories and possessions).

